{"tid":618370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你一直都揾緊代替品","createTime":"2018-04-05T18:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T04:07:50.000Z","uid":145427,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c413e0006140796f3571269549a30dccc2149ba9","tid":618370,"uid":145427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人係分手之後 以為放低左 點知開始另一段感情之後覺得呢個人有d唔係好夾<br />\n結果拍左一段好短既時間就散左<br />\n然後你遇到好多人 你以為好夾 但相處落又差感d野 結果拍左幾段散拖 <br />\n<br />\n其實你每開始一段新感情<br />\n你都會拎佢黎同前度比較 <br />\n你一直都活係佢既影子之下<br />\n因為你已經習慣左同佢既相處方式<br />\n<br />\n你可以忘記愛佢既感覺<br />\n但你忘記唔到習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以 唔好要人習慣左你之後又離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2e9ca669a142e2a48263ac29516aaa7327b53b","tid":618370,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"一絲不掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9732db8005ccdeeb1e1297d2779bca1b0de517d1","tid":618370,"uid":145427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f2e9ca669a142e2a48263ac29516aaa7327b53b","tid":618370,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"一絲不掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0c6465b79e1ea16ed74249d42ffa850bed9922","tid":618370,"uid":81053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90271bc3ef0de6a72aed115d4e7dadadc4725c67","tid":618370,"uid":115534,"like":0,"dislik